  levelName: "m\xE0n 3"
  introLines:
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "L\u0169 nh\u1EA7y nh\u1EE5a ch\u1EBFt ti\u1EC7t n\xE0y, t\u1EA1i sao b\u1ECDn
      ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i t\u1EDBi n\u1EEFa r\u1ED3i, sao c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c  b\u1ECDn
      ch\xFAng  l\u1EA1i kh\xE1c h\u01A1n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc n\u1EEFa nh\u1EC9!!!"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt ch\xFAng t\u1EEB \u0111\xE2u t\u1EDBi n\u1EEFa , t\u1EA1i
      sao c\xF3 c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c ch\xFAng ng\xE0y c\xE0ng kh\xE1c h\u01A1n n\u1EEFa
      v\u1EADy. Kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF3 \u1ED5n kh\xF4ng
      n\u1EEFa. \u0111\xE3 2 tu\u1EA7n tr\xF4i qua r\u1ED3i, sao m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
      ch\u01B0a quay tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 v\u1EADy."
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "M\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a v\u1EDBi  t\xF4i r\u1EB1ng
      s\u1EBD quay tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 v\u1EDBi t\xF4i m\xE0\u2026 Tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1
      ng\xF4i nh\xE0 b\xECnh y\xEAn c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng ta\u2026 t\u1EA1i sao v\u1EADy\u2026"
